Buildings

Indaco Metals buildings are designed to meet IBC requirements and conform to codes within city limits. Standard and custom options are available.  Learn More

 

Carports

Our fully engineered metal structural carports and patio covers provide a safe, customized shelter for your car or truck.  Learn More

 

Roofing

Indaco Metal's roofing products are built to last. They are safe, durable, cost-effective and maintain their color for years to come. Learn More

 


Indaco Solves

Previous Next

Flexibility, creativity, and choices.

In 2013, over 8,000 customers chose Indaco Metals for their purchase of metal buildings, metal roofing, metal building components and accessories, including our complete all-metal truss and rigid frame building packages, our three retail profiles of cut-to-length metal panels, as well as custom and standard trim. We also provide a full range of products for professional metal building and metal roofing contractors.
